        "content_html": "<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/00/0045f018499f4df38d9d225e3a59597e_2976_4209_780885.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>2026年5月1-3日<br>仙人掌音乐节，再度登陆武汉<br>“当多元音浪在荆楚大地交响”<br>“让此刻的共鸣直抵你我心脏”</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/462e27c31bbf49898b0017d1e475555d_730_1701_1593816.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>5月1日<br><br>★ 许巍<br>唱响诗意与远方</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/22073af2c2ed47648f644fd348992697_1080_2180_2906466.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>★ 郑钧<br>中国摇滚乐代表人物<br>归来仍是那个赤裸裸的</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/ecbfa71fc5484b7cb5f66e91d22f8bd3_1080_2180_2978107.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>★ 痛仰<br>中国摇滚的精神旗帜<br>一直往南方开，开到武汉</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/04679d84b24f4d5c85d2d5ce446c0066_1080_2180_3209798.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"1292\"></p>\n<p>★ 二手玫瑰<br>摇滚江湖的一枝独秀<br>五一假期 武汉“接客</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/bd85a5e31acd4777aa34c9fb53a43735_1080_2180_3930973.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>★ 老狼<br>校园民谣的代言人<br>跨越青春的国民歌手</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/2a81ccaef51b4c0789e54b88ba0006c9_1080_2180_3555076.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>★ 棱镜<br>流动音阶组合纯粹词句<br>以真诚口吻表达真切情感</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/d819286f9c3d483a9b0aa748b6b50601_1080_2180_2906020.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>★ 夏日入侵企画<br>一起赴一场夏日的约<br>我们在武汉也可以一起“去海边”</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/04795c6e3c9643a98636a3dce0522670_1080_2180_3945559.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>★ 张玮玮＆郭龙<br>当代民谣代表性人物<br>携手把西北的风沙吹成诗</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/46b6829abac443baa8d8cf941cd953c9_1080_2180_3490397.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>★ 声音玩具<br>华丽而诗意的摇滚乐</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/9ba5dc305a244e92bf09b2755eaa5176_1080_2180_2770038.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>★ 柳爽<br>自由洒脱的年轻歌者</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/8a85227a23c6460c82eca09db5191a16_1080_2180_3846830.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>★ 散人乐队<br>川渝摇滚的符号级新人</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/73b47404617341a690c6629e118a70ff_1080_2180_3511567.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>★ 耿斯汉<br>华语乐坛的摇滚唱将</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/ee4e924f26154e02850e41ee5a394878_1080_2180_3214799.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>5月2日</p>\n<p>★ 张震岳<br>华语乐坛自在如风的唱作人<br>跟着感觉走的真实记录者</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/263d415a1b2c4fddab5b9f3376c956aa_1080_2180_2738069.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>★ 大张伟<br>人间清醒的朋克少年<br>永远真诚 永远传递快乐</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/d8f26f5f85474cfe9956e7c7907e5b11_1080_2180_3396799.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"1292\"></p>\n<p>★ 林宥嘉<br>当代华语乐坛无法忽略的声音<br>温柔嗓音包裹的细致灵魂</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/f64065e5a7574233b867721dfe111441_1080_2180_3444149.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>★ 窦靖童<br>独具个性的华语女唱作人<br>在实验与流行的边界自由穿梭</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/dde748b0a05943ccb24b912b2a07f937_1080_2180_2934053.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"1292\"></p>\n<p>★ 戴佩妮<br>华语乐坛公认的唱作才女<br>获奖无数的金曲天后</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/7af9801fdd9c492eb24b66eb95572406_1080_2180_3441241.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"1292\"></p>\n<p>★ 魏如萱waa<br>是“末路狂花”也是“怪奇的珍珠”<br>抵达无数人心底的独特女声</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/545b636942e4413bb90893db44c47194_1080_2180_3046312.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>★ 杨乃文<br>特立独行的摇滚女爵<br>冷冽与炽热并存的另类女声</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/6b8e52c8d6034047b5e68e1e8f8d7301_1080_2180_626551.0x0.jpg?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"1292\"></p>\n<p>★ 落日飞车<br>宝岛原创音乐旗舰型乐团<br>一辆驶向世界的音乐列车</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/38a86a038fbe4818acd112cb5499b8b2_1080_2180_2800264.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>★ 霓虹花园<br>年轻无畏的新浪漫主义乐队<br>用最具生命力的现场点燃空气</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/59bd153f20e34baeba0517289972199f_1080_2180_3537205.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>★ 艾怡良<br>岁月吻过的温柔女声<br>唱出都市人的隐秘心事</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/b1be6779aafa429f88b327c854ae3322_1080_2180_3594515.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"1292\"></p>\n<p>★ ChiliChill乐团<br>极具创造力的二人音乐组合</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/386bb70f416c4ae5b2e3dcf67eee7f3e_1080_2180_3309018.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>★ 163braces<br>台湾Z世代创作女声<br>卧室里走出的超级新星</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/c5316ccd2f054ff888d095ed7f330477_1080_2180_3293008.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"1292\"></p>\n<p>5月3日</p>\n<p>★ GAI周延（D.M.G）<br>新华流说唱领军人物</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/5aad960decd548129683996e3d184ca2_1080_2180_3278010.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"1292\"></p>\n<p>★ C-BLOCK<br>「功夫胖KUNGFU-PEN / 盛宇D-SHINE / KEY.L刘聪」<br>湘江边走出的江湖传奇<br>把长沙刻入中文说唱版图<br><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/9d18f8d0ba6b4aefbaf869c47fb1afb6_1080_2180_2944116.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>★ TizzyT<br>独具个性与天赋的音乐人<br>保持进化与蜕变的少年心气</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/ed13778b86aa448b8ef736d94177e19c_1080_2180_3609268.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>★ 姜云升<br>兼具Rap Star气质和超强实力<br>近年最具突破及关注度的说唱歌手<br><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/030d0f3afc704a83828f152ef75b43a4_1080_2180_3019989.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>★ 沙一汀EL<br>才华横溢的少年说唱<br>用音乐记录Z世代情感</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/72dac67ab3f3489f9e0144846c7ed645_1080_2180_3431403.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>★ 艾志恒Asen<br>行业标杆级的说唱歌手<br>激励无数听众的小镇传奇</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/04624147f28341b095865eba75d15016_1080_2180_3362215.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>★ GALI<br>帅哥说唱代表<br>兼具先锋质感与街头态度<br><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/daa3d5f831c944109b2a1e9a0842ecab_1080_2180_3247055.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>★ 王齐铭WatchMe<br>重庆说唱的中流砥柱<br>将市井生活熬成一锅“麻辣烫”</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/3d8685799ffe4adf8822044dd8c0a19c_1080_2180_3427354.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"1292\"></p>\n<p>★ MULA SAKEE<br>浪潮之中保持真我<br>具有国际视野的Rap Star</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/f1405625ee6b4e5ab56f9920db7f6a96_1080_2180_3154249.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"1292\"></p>\n<p>★ Top Barry<br>2025最受瞩目的新生代Rapper<br>试图用年轻视角重新定义潮流</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/b3fca31418b94d018b6b00c8272abb8e_1080_2180_3668902.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>★华云龙KLE<br>中文方言说唱现象级黑马<br>短视频平台爆火的“山东王”</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/2417469ed149440fa1314fc029d907ca_1080_2180_3117747.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>★ 翁杰 Winjay<br>福建沿海走出的“莆田才子”<br>在城乡之间重构街头叙事</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/6546ade6c43e4366827cf7bdbb2ccd06_1080_2180_3499619.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>★ 陈一豪Clear<br>真诚叙事的治愈系少年<br>让长沙再次骄傲的实力新生代</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/7cb968ca4724458f9934f12e17eff253_1080_2180_3837418.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>★ 马赫mood<br>左手拿起画笔 &nbsp;右手拿起麦克风<br>街头画家用真实经历打磨每一个韵脚</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/407addc5936e44e58ab77c6dd8e456e0_1080_2180_2942322.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>（ACID）</p>\n<p>★ 极品贵公子 ＆ Udigg&amp;贾真 ＆ Africakid中文说唱新血代表</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0323/16/30/aae7732253a54730a69d0a169cc5e986_1080_2180_3541507.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"></p>"
